<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa, rumnak ka tum lo, Sui le ngun ka tum lo; Pathian ka kawl hmasa
 lai, Vancung luh ka duh ko; Nangmah umnak inn chungah, Nangmah catlap
 chungah, Jesuh Bawipa ka chim tuah, keimah min a um maw?

[C1]
   Keimah (keimah) min a (min a) um maw, na catlap ran chungah, Na
   pennak cauk (cauk) chungah (chungah), Keimah min a um maw? (um maw)

[V2]
 Rili thetse bantukin, Ka sualnak a tam ko, Na thi in, maw ka khamh tu,
 Ka sualnak na tlengh cang; &quot;Ka sualnak tam hmanhsehlaw, Hawhra rang
 bangtukin, A thiang cang,&quot; tiah na zangfahnak in bia na ka chimh.

[C2]
   Keimah (keimah) min a (min a) um maw, na catlap ran chungah, Na
   pennak cauk (cauk) chungah (chungah), Keimah min a um maw? (um maw)

[V3]
 A thiang, a tha khua chungah, Inn kha a ceu a tlang, A lian a ngan
 mithiang i aihmi puan kha a rang; Zei te tihnak um ti lo, Khi khua tha
 chungah khin, Vanmi an dirkamh nak ah, ka min aa tial ve ko.

[C3]
   Keimah (keimah) min a (min a) um maw, na catlap ran chungah, Na
   pennak cauk (cauk) chungah (chungah), Keimah min a um maw? (um maw)</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<title>KEIMAH MIN A UM MAW? CH330</title>
<hymn_number>330</hymn_number>
</song>